start phosgene

memory 1000 mb

geometry units angstroms
  O1     0.000     0.000     1.726
  C2     0.000     0.000     0.531
  Cl3    0.000     1.511    -0.500
  Cl4    0.000    -1.511    -0.500
end

basis
  O  library 6-31g
  C  library 6-31g
  Cl library 6-31g
end

dft
  mult 1 
  xc b3lyp
  maxiter 100
  print low
end

task dft

